translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: お前には大盛りにしてやんよ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'll give you a large serving!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ちょっ！？　なんで蜜柑乗せたー！？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Wait!? Why did you put a mandarin on top!?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あ、手が届かない！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah, I can't reach it!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あっ、ちょ、くっ……！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah, hey, ugh...!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 数分の苦戦の末に、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: After struggling for several minutes,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 長田君は頭の上から蜜柑をどかした。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Nagata moved the mandarin off his head.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: えー……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Umm...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この子意味分からない……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I don't understand this kid at all...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 最近の若者、怖いわー……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Young people these days are scary...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ま、まあ、飯が冷めない内に食おうぜ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: W-well, let's eat before the food gets cold.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなたは長田君と更に仲良くなれた気がした。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You felt you became even closer with Nagata.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: うひぃ……なんとか勝てた……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ugh... we somehow made it through...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 山賊、マジ怖すぎっしょ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Those bandits are seriously terrifying...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 本当だよ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Really...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あんなのに負けてたらどうなってたか……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I shudder to think what would have happened if we lost to them...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 考えただけでマジびびるわー！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Just thinking about it really freaks me out!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: マジ！？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Seriously!?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ……怖がってるように見えなかったからなぁ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...You didn't look scared though.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんだ、＜エール＞も本当は怖かったんだ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: So, <Aile>, you were actually scared too.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: うえっ……それ、マジで言ってる？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ugh... are you serious about that?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 余裕しゃくしゃくすぎっしょ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You act way too confident...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はあ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sigh...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王ランスが暴れ回る今の時代、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: In these times when Demon King Rance is rampaging,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 安全な場所なんてどこにもなくてさぁ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: There's nowhere that's truly safe anymore.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: みんな浮き足だってて、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Everyone is all unsettled,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それに乗っかって無法者も
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and the outlaws take advantage of that,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: やりたい放題なんだろうね……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: doing whatever they want, I guess...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: マジありえねぇー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Seriously, that's unacceptable.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: へっ？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Huh?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: へ？　なんでまた？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Huh? Why again?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＜エール＞が魔王を倒すから？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Because <Aile> is going to defeat the Demon King?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: もしかして
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Could it be

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王を倒すって……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: that you really mean to defeat the Demon King...?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: マジで言ってる？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Are you serious?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あ、マジで言ってんすか……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah, you're really saying that...?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ――って！　無理無理無理、無理だから！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: —No way! No way, no way! It's impossible!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王には絶対に勝てないから！？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You'll never be able to defeat the Demon King!?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: うは、＜エール＞お前、マジかぁ……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Whoa, <Aile>, are you for real...?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: えーと、じゃあ何？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Um, so then what?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今、俺達は魔王ランスがいるっていう
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Right now, we're heading to Mount Shoryu where Demon King Rance supposedly is,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 翔竜山に向かってるの？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Mount Shoryu?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんで魔王がいる場所知らねぇの！？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Why don't you know where the Demon King is!?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王ランスなら世界一高い山、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If it's Demon King Rance, he lives at the top of the tallest mountain in the world,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 翔竜山の山頂付近でお城作って
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Mount Shoryu, where he built a castle near the summit,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そこに暮らしてるよ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and he lives there.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ぶっちゃけ、＜エール＞じゃ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: To be honest, <Aile>, you absolutely can't win against him,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ぜーーったいに勝てないぜ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: there's no chance at all.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: え、仲間を集める？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Huh? Gather allies?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ま、まあ、それなら……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: W-well, if that's the case...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなたは、母から伝えられた、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You told him the plan your mother gave you,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスの子達を仲間にする作戦を教えた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: to recruit Rance's children as allies.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王の子と協力して、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Working together with the Demon King's children,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔王ランスを倒す……？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: to defeat Demon King Rance...?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: …………無理だぁ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...That's impossible.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いや、なにその顔！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: No, what's with that expression!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ――って！　無理無理無理、無理だから！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: —No way! No way, no way! It's impossible!

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Right now, we're heading to Mount Shoryu where Demon King Rance supposedly is,
